=== Granular Operation Benchmarks ===
Iterations per test: 5000

--- Arithmetic ---
Basic math (+, *, -): 9ms
Exponentiation (**): 9ms
Modulo (%): 9ms

--- Variable Access ---
Local var read: 8ms
Local var write: 7ms

--- Function Calls ---
Empty arrow fn call: 8ms
Arrow fn with args: 14ms
Named fn call: 13ms

--- Nested Functions ---
Nested fn call: 41ms
3-level nested fn: 46ms

--- Object Creation ---
Create 1-prop object: 10ms
Create 5-prop object: 18ms
Create object with exprs: 15ms

--- Object Access ---
Dot property read: 10ms
Dot property write: 9ms
Bracket property read: 11ms
Bracket property write: 9ms
Deep property chain (4): 13ms

--- Array Creation ---
Create 3-elem array: 9ms
Create 10-elem array: 11ms

--- Array Access ---
Array index read: 9ms
Array index write: 8ms
Array .length: 9ms

--- Array Methods ---
Array.push(): 11ms
Array.pop(): 11ms
Array.sort() (5 elems): 15ms
Array.map() (5 elems): 18ms
Array.filter() (5 elems): 19ms
Array.reduce() (5 elems): 42ms
Array.splice(): 13ms

--- Spread Operators ---
Array spread copy: 10ms
Array spread + concat: 10ms
Object spread copy: 13ms
Object spread + extend: 13ms

--- Destructuring ---
Array destructure (3): 12ms
Object destructure (2): 15ms

--- Object Statics ---
Object.assign(): 19ms
Object.keys(): 14ms
Object.values(): 15ms
Object.entries(): 15ms
Object.fromEntries(): 16ms

--- Loops ---
for loop (100x50): 8ms
while loop (100x50): 9ms
for-of loop (500x10): 6ms

--- Conditionals ---
if-else: 10ms
ternary: 9ms
switch (4 cases): 11ms

--- String Operations ---
String concat (+): 7ms
Template literal: 11ms
String.length: 9ms
String.toUpperCase(): 7ms
String.split(): 9ms

=== Granular Benchmarks Complete ===
